Vulnerable Systems:
SimpGB version 1.46.02

Vulnerability Type:
Program flaws - The product scripts have flaws which allow attackers to get access to the sensitive information. 

Vendor:
Bosch IT-Consulting

Vendor Status: 
The Vendor has confirmed the problem and has release new version 1.47 that addresses the problem. New version of product was tested and we can confirm that all vulnerabilities were solved.  For more information see vendor announcement. To download the latest version go to vendors product download area.
Workaround:
Delete the file "cfginfo.php".
Example: 
REQUEST:
http://[TARGET]/[PRODUCT DIRECTORY]/admin/cfginfo.php
REPLY:
The table with global variables will be disclosed.
